<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="horrible-adj">horrible <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'hɒrəbl/    美 /'hɔːrəbl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>可怕的；恐怖的</strong></h4>
<p>making you feel very shocked and frightened (terrible)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a horrible dream
可怕的梦</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>[非正式用语]极讨厌的；糟透的</strong></h4>
<p>very bad or unpleasant：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The food looked horrible, but it tasted OK.
那食物看上去很糟糕，但是尝起来还不错。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>What horrible weather!
这鬼天气!</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>horribly /'hɒrəbli/ adv   </p></div>